{"tid":835733,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙基利：利物浦該向拜仁學習","createTime":"2018-09-25T06:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T12:09:58.000Z","uid":161311,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"27ba36aec49b7ed93223b91afa921d2b962c37a4","tid":835733,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"《每日鏡報》報導，沙基利認為利物浦可以學習他的老東家拜仁，以結束29年的聯賽冠軍荒。<br />\n<br />\n　　沙基利曾在2013和2014年助拜仁奪取德甲冠軍，今夏他加盟利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n　　沙基利表示：「在拜仁，我們唯一的目標就是奪冠。利物浦是世界上最大的球會之一。上季他們表現非常出色，不幸的是沒有奪冠。現在我們要更上一層樓，以奪冠為目標。這是最重要的事情，也是我們的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我以前就認識高普，也知道他的足球風格，所以利物浦的規模並不讓我驚訝。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「從史篤城到利物浦的變化很大，但我知道如何為豪門效力，因為我曾效力過拜仁和國米。」<br />\n<br />\n　　拜仁拿到過28座德甲冠軍，過去14年拿到10座，而利物浦至今和英超冠軍無緣。"},{"pid":"eb290e7f93813abee1e95314333adb9f38cb4e10","tid":835733,"uid":198866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"依家國米仲算唔算豪門"},{"pid":"a68ed40fb08953b5594fad5e11f34cc0f1d0d501","tid":835733,"uid":206673,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">現在我們要更上一層樓，以奪冠為目標。</span><br />\n即係利記一直都唔係以套冠為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a891ab11d8ad9995f76b31a9dd6151df729c2fa0","tid":835733,"uid":4957,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"英冠球王<br />\n受教了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750dbe6e78db7a60c27ba28afdbd847b79063475","tid":835733,"uid":15394,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"呢條矮撚收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69655788e8b87544c1b35bb716eca2ffc37b4449","tid":835733,"uid":98659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5